{"tid":878940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再講「做咩都冇用」、「有咩用？」、「哦。」","createTime":"2018-10-27T14:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T15:57:28.000Z","uid":190579,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd1fc2fa0b45734d729c949c6c1d283c138c729","tid":878940,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"<em><strong>China is erasing its border with Hong Kong</strong></em><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQyxG4vTyZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMQyxG4vTyZ8&d=vBTfQxO9OeUepJqlu6n2%2F8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=252e62aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MQyxG4vTyZ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬有眼睇。老老實實刻下我諗冇人知道做咩係「有用」，條片拍左出嚟除左比D鬼佬無聊睇下share下都真係冇乜用。但你<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔講唔討論咩都唔做，就好快就冇人知道香港係咩情況，亦都係共產黨最期待既畫面。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n舉個例子，條片入面講六四晚會，鬼佬見到係impressed既。我知你想講咩，你想話呢個<br />\n1)只不過係飯民cap水大會<br />\n2)點解要理會鄰國民主<br />\n3)點蠟燭後和平散去有咩用<br />\n以上三點<span style=\"color: red;\">全部都有道理</span>，我主要既point唔係想合理化/宣傳個晚會，<span style=\"color: red;\">五毛唔好藉此轉移討論焦點</span>。<br />\n我只係想借嚟表達:<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">社會運動</span>(晚會)的確<span style=\"color: green;\">改變唔到政治現實</span>(六四仲未平反)，但另一個功能就係記錄歷史，<span style=\"color: green;\">話比人知有件咁既事發生過</span>(有心既鬼佬或者小朋友見到晚會就會去查下其實係咩一回事)<br />\n<br />\n和理非非又好，更積極既抗爭又好，其實刻下都係冇用，但都<span style=\"color: red;\">比咩都唔做，甚至互潑冷水好</span>，因為咩都唔做好快就冇人提。呢樣係中共最想見到，亦都喺背後積極做緊既事(e.g.主流媒體冇報美國領使館抗議，就知道中共唔想輿論討論)<br />\n<br />\n既然任何形式既抗爭都無法係短期帶嚟D咩實際影響，但起碼可以刺激討論，等鬼佬知道，同等香港人記得中共同香港政府對香港人做左D咩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇一個抗爭/革命/獨立/起義係一開波就成功，一定係受鎮壓先，但人地唔係一受鎮壓就諗「做咩都冇用」，而係keep住一有空間就盡可能抗爭+討論，到最後外在條件允許下(外國介入/本國政權失勢/武裝起義)先爆發。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你唔認同人地既抗爭方式(太和平/太激進)，就用自己既方式抗爭，比起坐係電腦前面打「做咩都冇用」、「有咩用？」、「哦。」點都有用小小。</span></span>"},{"pid":"fa47b67fa5206b9f134d81908c52625c18e286a5","tid":878940,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd41071f75045bc8f16a4c8b1190472c30d9e035","tid":878940,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},{"pid":"45da32cdec5c5030efa2d93acef85cc0964b470a","tid":878940,"uid":146805,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cd41071f75045bc8f16a4c8b1190472c30d9e035","tid":878940,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"玩左咁多年都係呢句，悶啦"},{"pid":"f9ddef1da5b42860027788ee342bd8c5c65c03a9","tid":878940,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"d3329ca591981abbeaf1c0bec7bced71badb089e","tid":878940,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"45da32cdec5c5030efa2d93acef85cc0964b470a","tid":878940,"uid":146805,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cd41071f75045bc8f16a4c8b1190472c30d9e035","tid":878940,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:04:24.000Z","msg":"玩左咁多年都係呢句，悶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:06:23.000Z","msg":"港獨猛將帶頭講先 支持港獨既我唔講呢句講邊句?"},{"pid":"ebc34366978155b9b2d9475b423d3b903aafdfa9","tid":878940,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd41071f75045bc8f16a4c8b1190472c30d9e035","tid":878940,"uid":197765,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"加埋「返工不了」"},{"pid":"d91337752a64ea111e02e7415519da58217c383a","tid":878940,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:12:48.000Z","msg":"係咩？碰！"},{"pid":"081178b93701b18680265edcbceb67e12fc078bc","tid":878940,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"連登仔最叻呢頭鬧完左膠泛民，轉個頭就搏命正皮d「唔好撥冷水」嘅post扮到好有建設性咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d5fd76f670ad4a9e9da73869e24371c0302116","tid":878940,"uid":88862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bb0db836d3695028b5719a6f94340abcd7afb86","tid":878940,"uid":53592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}